{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "This is where I learned love.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "This is where I learned joy for life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "This is where I learned who I was, and who I must remain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And really, it served me, I think, as a very, very important tool for survival, I think.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "I'm saying that in, in reflecting as an adult woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how conscious it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "It probably was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "But I do remember distinctly how we all conjured up-- even when we were in the barracks or under the worst of circumstances, we conjured up our past, that we remembered the warmth and the wonderfulness of home.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And I think that that very much carried us through and laid the core in us of humanity.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And I think, I hope, we passed it on to our progeny.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family was-- had a very strong identification of Jewishness, but they were not-- they were not observing it regularly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Saturday was special.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On holidays, often we went-- well, not very often, but on high holidays sometimes we did go to the temple.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The times that stand out in my mind especially is during Symcha's Torah because I loved the, the, the, the little flags with the apple on top.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was such a joyful holiday, that I remember we did go to-- these are the times that I recall at the temple most vividly, yes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had very little formal schooling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And really, my formal schooling began as an adult in the United States when I started to go to the university.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Between that and my schooling as a child was-- I had three years of formal education, first, second, and third grade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the invasion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And schools were closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a public school, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
